JSHOP2

Class Predicate

  • java.lang.Object
    • JSHOP2.CompileTimeObject
      • JSHOP2.Predicate

  • public class Predicate
extends CompileTimeObject
    Each predicate, both at compile time and at run time, is an instance of this class.
    Version:
    1.0.3
    Author:
    Okhtay Ilghami, http://www.cs.umd.edu/~okhtay

      • head

      • param

        The argument list of this predicate.

      • varCount

        private int varCount
        The number of variables in this predicate. Used to return a binding of the appropriate size.

      • varIdx

        private int varIdx
        In case this predicate is a variable symbol and not a real atom, this represents its index. Otherwise, its value will be -1.

      • staticID

        private static int staticID
        A unique ID to identify this predicate. Used in conjunction with JSHOP2GUI to allow it to discern exactly which task atom is being referenced at every step of the plan finding process.

        private int ID

        public java.lang.String toString()
